tournament.name: NYC Mid-Atlantic Circuit 2025
tournament.description: New York City's first edition of the Mid-Atlantic Circuit! Come enjoy the city during the holidays and play at a new space hosted by NYC Resistor!
tournament.registration_message:
## 🚨 PLEASE READ THESE NOTES FIRST 🚨
> 📝 You can change your information at any time while registration is open.

> 💸 We are asking anyone who is able to please contribute ANY AMOUNT to the community support fund. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form 

> ❤️ If you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due.

> 👀 Spectators will not be charged entry but do need to register so you can be included on the attendee list as NYC Resistor is a private space. Fill out the form including the spectator checkbox below and click save info instead of going through payment.

> 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 If your team's name is not finalized, select Free Agent and return later to create your team. Be sure to check if your team already exists before creating a new one.

> 🧾 We are using Stripe to accept payments. Stripe securely stores your personal data and it will not be used or shared with anyone other than to process the payment.

### If you have any questions, please reach out to Tyler (tyler13) or Alex (bacongames) on Discord!
tournament.payment_message: To cover venue and cabinet logistics costs, we are asking attendees to pay a registration fee of $20.
